org.apache.flink.runtime.state.heap

类 CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry<K,N,S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.state.heap.CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry<K,N,S>
  • 类型参数:
    K - type of key.
    N - type of namespace.
    S - type of state.
    所有已实现的接口:
    StateEntry<K,N,S>
    封闭类:
    CopyOnWriteStateTable<K,N,S>

    static class CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry<K,N,S>
extends java.lang.Object
implements StateEntry<K,N,S>
    One entry in the CopyOnWriteStateTable. This is a triplet of key, namespace, and state. Thereby, key and namespace together serve as a composite key for the state. This class also contains some management meta data for copy-on-write, a pointer to link other CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntrys to a list, and cached hash code.

    • 字段详细资料

      • key

        final K key
        The key. Assumed to be immutable and not null.

      • namespace

        final N namespace
        The namespace. Assumed to be immutable and not null.

      • state

        S state
        The state. This is not final to allow exchanging the object for copy-on-write. Can be null.

      • next

        CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry<K,N,S> next
        Link to another CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry. This is used to resolve collisions in the CopyOnWriteStateTable through chaining.

      • entryVersion

        int entryVersion
        The version of this CopyOnWriteStateTable.StateTableEntry. This is meta data for copy-on-write of the table structure.

      • stateVersion

        int stateVersion
        The version of the state object in this entry. This is meta data for copy-on-write of the state object itself.

      • hash

        final int hash
        The computed secondary hash for the composite of key and namespace.
